%3EDelhi%20government%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20additional%20water%20supply%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20for%20a%20month%20amid%20a%20severe%20shortage%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20petition%20in%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Delhi%20said%20that%20the%20need%20for%20water%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20amid%20sweltering%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi's%20need%20for%20water%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20scorching%20heat.%20It%20is%20everyone's%20responsibility%20to%20fulfill%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Minister%20Atishi%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20Centre%20claiming%20that%20Haryana%20has%20not%20been%20releasing%20the%20required%20amount%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20water%20from%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20for%20its%20day-to-day%20demand%20for%20water.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20drastic%20dip%20in%20the%20water%20levels%20at%20the%20Wazirabad%20Barrage%20as%20Haryana%20is%20not%20releasing%20the%20required%20amount%20of%20water%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20river%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20Union%20Water%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20the%20temperature%20in%20Delhi%20has%20touched%20almost%2050%20degrees.%20This%20has%20further%20intensified%20the%20demand%20for%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20areas%20in%20Delhi%20including%20Chanakyapuri's%20Sanjay%20Camp%20area%20and%20the%20Geeta%20colony%20area%20among%20those%20facing%20acute%20water%20shortages.%20In%20the%20blazing%20heat%2C%20people%20wait%20in%20long%20queues%2C%20hoping%20to%20fill%20at%20least%20one%20bucket%2C%20as%20tankers%20come%20and%20go%20without%20adequately%20serving%20the%20large%20populations%20in%20the%20colonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20crisis%20in%20Delhi%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20maximum%20temperature%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20is%20inching%20close%20to%20the%2050%20degrees%20Celsius%20mark.%20The%20minimum%20temperature%20is%20nearly%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%202.8%20degrees%20above%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20said%20heatwave%20conditions%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20will%20persist%20for%20the%20next%20few%20days%20and%20advised%20people%20to%20minimise%20exposure%20to%20heat%20and%20stay%20hydrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP-led%20Delhi%20government%20on%20Wednesday%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20on%20wastage%20of%20water%20and%20formed%20200%20teams%20to%20enforce%20the%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717142160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fdelhi-water-crisis_625x300_1530181536010.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-government-requests-supreme-court-for-additional-water-supply-from-haryana-up-and-himachal-for-a-month-amid-crisis-5784518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20government%20requests%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20additional%20water%20supply%20from%20Haryana%2C%20UP%2C%20and%20Himachal%20for%20a%20month%20amid%20crisis%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-government-requests-supreme-court-for-additional-water-supply-from-haryana-up-and-himachal-for-a-month-amid-crisis-5784518%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-government-requests-supreme-court-for-additional-water-supply-from-haryana-up-and-himachal-for-a-month-amid-crisis-5784518%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-government-requests-supreme-court-for-additional-water-supply-from-haryana-up-and-himachal