osure%20of%20his%20Twitter%20stake%20to%20amass%20shares%20at%20lower%20prices.%20The%20Oklahoma%20firefighters%20pension%20fund%20said%20Musk%20saved%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%20by%20adding%20to%20his%20Twitter%20stake%20in%20secret%2C%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20some%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Birchall%20enlisted%20the%20unidentified%20managing%20director%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20to%20develop%20a%20clandestine%20trading%20strategy%20to%20hide%20Musk's%20Twitter%20stock%20acquisition%20and%20allow%20him%20to%20buy%20shares%20at%20%26quot%3Bartificially%20depressed%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Musk%20nor%20Birchall%20were%20immediately%20available%20for%20comment.%20Morgan%20Stanley%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMorgan%20Stanley%20is%20not%20a%20defendant%20in%20this%20lawsuit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Morgan%20Stanley%20executive%20repeatedly%20told%20Birchall%20to%20seek%20legal%20advice%20regarding%20the%205%25%20disclosure%20requirements%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%20Birchall%20told%20the%20executive%20that%20lawyers%20had%20been%20consulted%2C%20when%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case%20until%20he%20had%20amassed%20over%20a%209%25%20stake%20in%20Twitter%20on%20April%201%2C%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20eventually%20bought%20Twitter%20for%20%2444%20billion%20in%20October%202022%20and%20changed%20the%20company's%20name%20to%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20knew%20the%20answer%2C%20they%20had%20to%20disclose%20but%20did%20not%20want%20to%2C%20in%20part%20because%20it%20would%20make%20Musk's%20purchases%20drastically%20more%20expensive%20and%20public%2C%20so%20Birchall%20and%20Musk%20disregarded%20repeated%20warnings%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Morgan%20Stanley%20executive%20%26quot%3Babout%20the%20need%20to%20get%20legal%20advice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20lawyers%20previously%20argued%20that%20their%20client%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20busiest%20people%20on%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20any%20disclosure%20failure%20was%20%26quot%3Binadvertent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violation%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20latest%20episode%20in%20Musk's%20history%20of%20disregard%20for%20the%20federal%20securities%20laws%20and%20contempt%20for%20the%20SEC%20and%20its%20rules%20and%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20the%20top%20U.S.%20markets%20regulator%20have%20been%20in%20a%20years-long%20feud%2C%20dating%20back%20to%202018%2C%20when%20he%20tweeted%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bfunding%20secured%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20electric%20carmaker%20Tesla%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717139940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fq4eqh9g8_elon-musk_625x300_24_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-disregarded-warnings-hid-twitter-stake-claims-us-lawsuit-5782820%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20ignored%20repeated%20warnings%20about%20the%20U.S.%20securities%20disclosure%20obligations%20potentially%20triggered%20by%20his%20growing%20stake%20in%20Twitter%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20executive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-disregarded-warnings-hid-twitter-stake-claims-us-lawsuit-5782820%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-disregarded-warnings-hid-twitter-stake-claims-us-lawsuit-5782820%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-disregarded-warnings-hid-twitter-stake-claims