%20after%20his%20arrest%20in%20Georgia%20over%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%2C%20when%20a%20widely%20publicized%20mug%20shot%20was%20taken%20at%20Fulton%20County%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat's%20less%20clear%20is%20how%20wealthy%20donors%20and%20business%20interest%20will%20react%20to%20the%20verdict.%20The%20campaign%20worked%20to%20ramp%20up%20fundraisers%20with%20mega-donors%20in%20April%20and%20May%2C%20seeking%20to%20raise%20money%20before%20a%20jury%20decision%20that%20could%20dissuade%20deep-pocketed%20donors%20from%20contributing%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20campaign's%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonor%20Decisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaun%20Maguire%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20which%20has%20backed%20several%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20companies%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20donating%20%24300%2C000%20to%20Trump%20after%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20timing%20isn't%20a%20coincidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Maguire%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Musk's%20social%20network.%20%26quot%3BThe%20media%20will%20probably%20demonize%20me%2C%20as%20they%20have%20so%20many%20others%20before%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20despite%20this%2C%20I%20still%20believe%20it's%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20The%20sentiment%20was%20lauded%20by%20Trump%20donor%20David%20Sacks%2C%20another%20venture%20capital%20investor%2C%20who%20is%20holding%20a%20fundraiser%20for%20the%20former%20president%20at%20his%20San%20Francisco%20home%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20fundraising%20operation%20has%20notched%20several%20wins%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20including%20raising%20%2476%20million%20in%20April%2C%20%2425%20million%20more%20than%20Biden%20raised%20that%20month.%20He's%20also%20garnered%20the%20support%20of%20billionaire%20Miriam%20Adelson%20and%20Blackstone%20Inc.%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Steve%20Schwarzman%2C%20two%20