s%2C%20Order%20Police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20complaints%20during%20vehicle%20checking%20at%20night%2C%20Gurugram%20DCP%20Traffic%20has%20issued%20instructions%20not%20to%20issue%20challans%20to%20vehicles%20at%20night%2C%20so%20that%20the%20drivers%20do%20not%20face%20any%20problems%20at%20night.%20If%20necessary%2C%20the%20permission%20of%20higher%20authorities%20will%20have%20to%20be%20obtained%2C%20only%20after%20which%20the%20challan%20can%20be%20issued%2C%20DCP%20Traffic%20issued%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Virendra%20Vij%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20May%2028%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BTraffic%20Inspectors%20are%20ordered%20to%20command%20all%20the%20employees%20appointed%20under%20them%20in%20their%20jurisdiction%20that%20no%20vehicle%20should%20be%20stopped%20at%20night%20and%20no%20challan%20should%20be%20issued.%20If%20it%20is%20very%20necessary%20to%20issue%20a%20challan%20to%20a%20driver%20as%20per%20the%20M.V.%20Act%2C%20in%20that%20situation%2C%20the%20challan%20of%20that%20vehicle%20should%20be%20issued%20as%20per%20rules%20only%20after%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20concerned%20gazetted%20officer%2Fundersigned%20and%20obtaining%20permission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCP%20has%20also%20warned%20that%20if%20any%20policeman%20does%20not%20follow%20the%20rules%2C%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20orders%20should%20be%20strictly%20followed.%20In%20case%20of%20negligence%20and%20carelessness%2C%20strict%20departmental%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20concerned%20traffic%20police%20officer%20as%20per%20rules%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20traffic%20movement%20at%20night%20in%20the%20district%20Gurugram%20and%20to%20resolve%20the%20inconveniences%20faced%20by%20common%20people%20during%20road%20travel%2C%20night%20traffic%20police%20personnel%20were%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20has%20come%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20undersigned%20that%20the%20traffic%20police%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20night%20are%20unnecessarily%20stopping%20the%20vehicles%20of%20common%20people%20and%20harassing%20them%20and%20are%20also%20unnecessarily%20issuing%20challans%20for%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirendra%20Vij%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20job%20of%20traffic%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20night%20was%20to%20help%20the%20common%20people%20and%20drivers%20and%20to%20arrange%20safe%20routes%20in%20case%20of%20a%20road%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20traffic%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20night%20should%20play%20an%20important%20role%20as%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20Gurugram%20by%20guiding%20and%20helping%20the%20common%20people%20and%20drivers%20and%20arranging%20safe%20routes%20to%20take%20them%20to%20their%20destinations%20and%20in%20case%20of%20a%20road%20accident.%20The%20injured%20persons%20should%20be%20immediately%20admitted%20to%20the%20nearest%20trauma%20center%20and%20the%20accident-hit%20vehicles%20should%20be%20immediately%20removed%20from%20the%20main%20road%20and%20traffic%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20run%20smoothly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20this%20order%20from%20the%20DCP%20of%20Gurugram%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20people%20have%20started%20flouting%20traffic%20rules.%20It%20is%20often%20seen%20that%20at%20night%2C%20people%20drive%20at%20high%20speed%20and%20recklessly%20on%20the%20roads%20of%20Gurugram%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCP%20Virendra%20Vij%20has%20informed%20that%20the%20traffic%20police%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20strict%20against%20drunk%20drivers%20at%20night%20so%20that%20no%20major%20accidents%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20three%20to%20four%20days%20a%20we