rds%20correctly%20in%20the%20tiebreaker%2C%20maintaining%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20children%20from%20the%20small%20ethnic%20community%20in%20the%20prestigious%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBruhat%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20the%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee%20on%20Thursday%2C%20earning%20more%20than%20%2450%2C000%20in%20cash%20and%20other%20prizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20contest%20came%20down%20to%20a%20tiebreaker%20in%20which%20Bruhat%20spelt%2029%20words%20correctly%20in%2090%20seconds%2C%20beating%20Faizan%20Zaki%2C%20who%20managed%20to%20correctly%20spell%2020%20words%20in%20the%20lightning%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20championship%20word%20was%20%E2%80%9Cabseil%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20is%20defined%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdescent%20in%20mountaineering%20by%20means%20of%20a%20rope%20looped%20over%20a%20projection%20above.%E2%80%9D%20Bruhat%20went%20first%20in%20the%20tiebreaker%2C%20and%20after%20he%20got%20through%2030%20words%2C%20it%20appeared%20he%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20beat.%20Faizan's%20pace%20was%20more%20uneven%20at%20the%20outset.%20He%20attempted%2025%20words%20but%20flubbed%20four%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBruhat%20Soma%20rules%20the%20word!%20The%20Champion%20of%20the%202024%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee!%20The%20boy%20with%20the%20unbelievable%20memory%20doesn't%20miss%20a%20word%20all%20week%20and%20takes%20home%20the%20Scripps%20Cup!%E2%80%9D%20the%20organisers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBruhat%20Soma%20correctly%20spelt%2029%20out%20of%2030%20words%20attempted%20to%20earn%20the%20coveted%20champion%20title%20and%20beat%20the%20standing%20spell-off%20record%20set%20by%20Harini%20Logan%20in%202022.%20Logan%20spelt%2022%20out%20of%2026%20words%20correctly%20during%20the%20competition's%20first-ever%20spell-off%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organisers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20competition%20progressed%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20Faizan%20and%20Bruhat%20%E2%80%93%20our%20final%20two%20spellers%20%E2%80%93%20showed%20up%20tonight%20ready%20to%20take%20down%20the%20dictionary%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Corrie%20Loeffler%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Bee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTogether%2C%20they%20were%20a%20powerful%20match.%20Bee%20officials%20activated%20the%20spell-off%20in%20the%20competition's%20closing%20minutes%2C%20giving%20these%20stellar%20spellers%20an%20opportunity%20to%20show%20even%20more%20of%20what%20they%20can%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Loeffler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20final%20spellers%20each%20had%2090%20seconds%20to%20spell%20as%20many%20words%20as%20they%20could%20from%20a%20predetermined%20list%20of%20words%20while%20the%20other%20speller%20was%20sequestered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20Symson%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20The%20E%20W%20Scripps%20Company%2C%20presented%20Bruhat%20with%20the%20championship%20trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20just%2012%20years%20old%2C%20Bruhat%20impressed%20with%20his%20display%20of%20knowledge%20and%20composure%2C%E2%80%9D%20Symson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20Bruhat's%20third%20time%20participating%20in%20the%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee.%20He%20tied%20for%2074th%20in%202023%20and%20tied%20for%20163rd%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaki%20of%20Allen%2C%20Texas%2C%20received%20USD%2025%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrey%20Parikh%20of%20Rancho%20Cucamonga%2C%20California%2C%20tied%20for%20third%20place%20in%20the%20competition%20received%20USD%2012%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnanya%20Prassanna%20of%20Apex%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20tied%20for%20third%20place%20in%20the%20competition%20and%20received%20USD%2012%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoached%20by%2016-year-old%20former%20speller%20Sam%20Evans%2C%20Bruhat%20previously%20competed%20in%202022%20(tied%20for%20163rd%20place)%20and%202023%20(tied%20for%2074th%20place).%20A%20multifaceted%20person%20with%20many%20interests%20and%20hobbies%2C%20he%20had%20previously%20won%20the%20Words%20of%20Wisdom%20Bee%20and%20SpellPundit%20Bee%20before%20arriving%20in%20a%20Maryland%20suburb%20of%20Washington%20DC%20for%20a%20prestigious%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBruhat's%20father%20Srinivas%20Soma%20is%20originally%20from%20Nalgonda%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee%20had%20eight%20finalists%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20were%20Indian-Americans%3A%20Rishabh%20Saha%2C%2014%20and%20Shrey%20Parikh%2C%2012%2C%20from%20California%3B%20Aditi%20Muthukumar%2C%2013%2C%20from%20Colorado%3B%20and%20Ananya%20Rao%20Prassanna%2C%2013%2C%20from%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian-American%20Dev%20Shah%20won%20last%20year's%20Bee%20by%20correctly%20spelling%20%26quot%3Bpsammophile.%26quot%3B%20Harini%20Logan%20had%20won%20the%20championship%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee%20is%20the%20nation's%20largest%20and%20longest-running%20educational%20programme%2C%20having%20been%20launched%20in%201925.%20It%20is%20a%20high-profile%2C%20high-pressure%20endurance%20test%20as%20much%20as%20a%20nerd%20spelling%20match%20and%20spellers%20spend%20months%20preparing%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bee%20was%20cancelled%20in%202020%20due%20to%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic.%20There%20were%20eight%20co-champions%20in%202019%2C%20seven%20of%20whom%20were%20Indian-Americans.%20Twenty-nine%20Indian-Americans%20have%20emerged%20as%20champions%20in%20the%20competition%20since%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20there%20were%20245%20spellers%20who%20came%20to%20participate%20in%20this%20year's%20competition%20sixty-five%20spellers%20had%20previously%20competed%20in%20the%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee.%20As%20many%20as%2024%20spellers%2C%20mostly%20Indian%20Americans%2C%20had%20relatives%20who%20had%20participated%20in%20a%20combined%2040%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%202023%20finalists%20advanced%20to%20the%202024%20national%20competition%3A%20Sarah%20Fernandes%2C%20tied%20for%2010th%20place%3B%20Aryan%20Khedkar%20tied%20for%20fifth%3B%20Tarini%20Nandakumar%2C%20finished%20ninth%3B%20and%20Shradha%20Rachamreddy%2C%20tied%20for%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAliyah%20Alpert%20and%20Kirsten%20Santos%20were%20finalists%20in%202022.%20Indian%20American%20Akash%20Vukoti%20has%20qualified%20for%20a%20record%20six%20finals%20in%202016%2C%202018%2C%202019%2C%202021%2C%202022%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717129020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpin813ic_bruhat-soma-spelling-bee_625x300_31_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F12-year-old-indian-american-bruhat-soma-wins-national-spelling-bee-contest-in-us-5784094%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bruhat%20Soma%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20Indian-American%20seventh-grade%20student%20from%20Florida%2C%20has%20won%20the%20Scripps%20National%20Spelling%20Bee%20after%20he%20spelt%2029%20words%20correctly%20in%20the%20tiebreaker.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F12-year-old-indian-american-bruhat-soma-wins-national-spelling-bee-contest-in-us-5784094%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F12-year-old-indian-american-bruhat-soma-wins-national-spelling-bee-contest-in-us-5784094%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F12-year-old-indian-american-bruhat-soma-wins-national-spelling-bee-contest-in-us-5784094%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eminem%20Releases%20New%20Single%20%E2%80%98Houdini%E2%80%99%20Referencing%20Megan%20Thee%20Stallion%2C%20Steve%20Miller%20Band%20and%202002%20Single%20%E2%80%98Without%20Me%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%2