le%20information%20that%20a%20yagya%20(special%20worship)%20is%20being%20conducted%20by%20'Aghoris'%20in%20an%20isolated%20place%20near%20the%20Rajarajeshwari%20temple%20in%20Kerala.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ritual%20is%20underway%20and%20is%20being%20conducted%20against%20me%2C%20the%20CM%2C%20and%20to%20destabilize%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reiterated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20objective%20of%20the%20yagya%20is%20to%20eliminate%20enemies%2C%20and%20the%20ritual%20is%20called%20'Raja%20Kantaka'%20and%20'Marana%20Mohana%20Stambhana'%20yagyas.%20Those%20participating%20in%20the%20ritual%20informed%20about%20this%20development%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20through%20the%20Aghoris%2C%2021%20red%20goats%2C%20three%20buffaloes%2C%2021%20black%20sheep%2C%20and%20five%20pigs%20are%20being%20sacrificed%20for%20black%20magic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20leaders%20from%20the%20BJP%20or%20JD-S%20are%20carrying%20out%20this%20ritual%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20maintained%20that%20politicians%20from%20Karnataka%20are%20responsible.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20who%20is%20conducting%20this%20ritual.%20Let%20them%20continue%20their%20efforts%3B%20I%20don't%20bother.%20It%20is%20left%20to%20their%20belief%20system.%20Despite%20their%20attempts%20and%20experiments%20to%20cause%20harm%2C%20the%20force%20which%20I%20believe%20in%20will%20protect%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%20about%20whether%20he%20will%20conduct%20a%20counter-worship%20to%20this%20ritual%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20pray%20to%20God%20for%20a%20minute%20every%20day%20before%20going%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20pressed%20to%20name%20the%20persons%20carrying%20out%20such%20a%20ritual%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20suggested%20that%20the%20media%20investigate%20rather%20than%20force%20him%20to%20reveal%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%2