app%20that%20lets%20people%20come%20together%20in%20virtual%20meetings.%20As%20few%20as%20two%20or%20as%20many%20as%20100%20participants%20can%20join%20the%20same%20meeting%20and%20can%20speak%2C%20communicate%20via%20chat%2C%20or%20share%20video%20with%20each%20other%20from%20anywhere%20with%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20designed%20the%20platform%20primarily%20for%20businesses%20and%20other%20organizations%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20great%20way%20for%20colleagues%20who%20don't%20work%20in%20the%20same%20location%20to%20communicate.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20used%20as%20a%20video%20platform%20connecting%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20of%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0Google%20Meet%C2%A0organizer%20can%20share%20whatever%20is%20on%20their%20screen%20with%20everyone%20on%20a%20call%2C%20and%20any%20participant%20can%20turn%20their%20own%20audio%20and%2For%20video%20feed%20off%20at%20any%20time%2C%20participating%20however%20they%20choose.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20enhanced%20the%20service%2C%20including%20visual%20effects%20to%20fix%20low%20video%20quality%20and%20lighting%20issues%20and%20translated%20captions%20for%20participants%20with%20language%20barriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20video-conferencing%20platforms%2C%20Google%20Meet%20exploded%20in%20popularity%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sundar%20Pichai%20announced%20in%20April%202020%20that%20Google%20Meet%20was%20adding%20roughly%203%20million%20users%20every%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20how%20to%20use%20the%20platform%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cca30e9-c36f-4b54-826a-7086afb071be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20Google%20Meet%20costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20business%20owner%20in%20a%20coffee%20shop%20smiles%20while%20typing%20on%20his%20laptop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6657677b1cd3b177904140b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20Meet%20has%20a%20free%20tier%2C%20but%20you'll%20need%20to%20pay%20for%20premium%20if%20you%20want%20to%20unlock%20longer%20meetings%2C%20or%20invite%20large%20numbers%20of%20participants.%3Cp%3EMilos%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Meet%20has%20a%20free%20tier%20that%20lets%20anyone%20with%20a%20Google%20account%20create%20or%20join%20a%20call%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there%20are%20some%20limitations.%20Group%20meetings%20can't%20exceed%2060%20minutes%20and%20can't%20have%20more%20than%20100%20participants%20(one-on-one%20meetings%20and%20mobile%20calls%20have%20no%20time%20limit).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Google%20offers%20pricing%20plans%20for%20organizations%20or%20individuals%20who%20need%20more%20flexibility%20with%20their%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Workspace%20has%20a%20few%20different%20membership%20tiers%2C%20and%20the%20more%20you%20pay%2C%20the%20more%20people%20you%20can%20have%20on%20a%20single%20Google%20Meet%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Starter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20costs%20%246%20a%20month%20per%20user.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20meet%20with%20up%20to%20100%20people%20at%20once%20for%20up%20to%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0costs%20%2412%20a%20month%20per%20user.%20You%20can%20meet%20with%20up%20to%20150%20people%20at%20once.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Plus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0costs%20%2418%20a%20month%20per%20user.%20With%20this%2C%20you%20can%20meet%20with%20up%20to%20500%20people%20at%20once.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnterprise%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20no%20fixed%20price%20and%20require