ccessibility%20for%20disabled%20persons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20for%20Digital%20Accessibility%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwebaim.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWebAIM%20(Web%20Accessibility%20in%20Mind).%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20GAAD%2C%20impacted%20communities%20worldwide%20make%20the%20case%20for%20digital%20accessibility%20for%20diverse%20disabilities.%20There%20are%20approximately%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20billion%20Persons%20with%20Disability%20(PwD)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20creating%20accessible%20digital%20technology%20is%20important%20from%20a%20civil%20rights%20as%20well%20as%20a%20business%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656-300x157.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656-500x262.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656-768x402.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656-150x79.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351277%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E