Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F1lhwATLxZKM%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%20invents%20a%20Solar%20powered%20Weed%20Killing%20Machine%20%23svc%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-tasking%20machine%20can%20perform%20four%20critical%20farming%20operations%20%E2%80%93%20cleaning%20weeds%2C%20drilling%20seeds%2C%20spraying%20fertiliser%20and%20laying%20manure.%20It%20works%20on%20both%20solar%20power%20and%20has%20a%20battery%2C%20for%20cloudy%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20customised%20for%20length%20and%20folded%20for%20easy%20transportation.%20The%20design%20incorporates%20easily%20adjustable%20parts%20and%20attachments%20that%20mimic%20the%20functionality%20of%20larger%2C%20more%20expensive%20farming%20machinery%2C%20making%20it%20an%20ideal%20solution%20for%20small-scale%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20can%20do%20all%20these%20different%20tasks%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20saving%20time%20and%20energy.%20You%20can%20remove%20weeds%20and%20spray%20fertilisers%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20It%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20picking%20up%20heavy%20spray%20tanks%20and%20hiring%20labourers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramdhan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20bulb%20for%20farmers%20who%20wish%20to%20work%20at%20night%20and%20has%20a%20charger%20for%20the%20battery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamdhan%E2%80%99s%20father%20beams%20with%20pride%20as%20he%20speaks%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-ag