C%20earthquakes%20and%20fires%20destroyed%20the%20other%20six.%20The%20Mausoleum%20of%20Halicarnauss%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20successive%20earthquakes%20between%20the%2011th%20and%2015th%20century%20CE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20heyday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297140%2Fwomen-queens-built-stepwells-india-architecture-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20monument%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20tomb%20of%20Mausolus%2C%20ruler%20of%20Caria%20(a%20region%20in%20present-day%20Turkey).%20But%20neither%20the%20devastating%20remains%20of%20stone%20it%20left%20behind%20nor%20the%20clouds%20of%20dust%20could%20erase%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20towering%20marble%20beauty%20that%20people%20would%20once%20gape%20at%20in%20pure%20wonder.%20The%20mammoth%20facade%20blended%20the%20ideas%20of%20Greek%20architects%20Pythius%20and%20Satyros%2C%20with%20sculptures%20flanking%20its%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20beauty%20personified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20palace%20on%20Muktaram%20Babu%20Street%20in%20North%20Kolkata%20(previously%20Calcutta%2C%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20British%20Raj)%2C%20is%20said%20to%20inspire%20the%20same%20reaction.%20While%20people%20have%20pointed%20out%20a%20resemblance%20between%20the%20Marble%20Palace%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20the%20monument%20in%20Turkey%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20any%20sound%20proof%20whether%20the%20latter%20inspired%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20architectural%20emblem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mansion%20that%20fuses%20cultures.%20This%20moniker%20aptly%20describes%20the%20Marble%20Palace%3B%20a%20white%20beacon%20of%20serenity%20set%20against%20a%20bustling%20stretch%20of%20land%20dotted%20with%20shops%20and%20bazaars.%20With%20its%20neoclassical%20architecture%20rising%20to%20the%20skies%20and%20its%20manor-like%20gates%20opening%20up%20a%20portal%20into%20an%20alternate%20dimension%20%E2%80%94%20a%20royal%20one%20if%20you%20will%20%E2%80%94%20the%20palace%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best-preserved%20private%20spaces%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4s4UlKStVk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4s4UlKStVk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4s4UlKStVk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Adrija%20Ghosal%20%7CKolkata%20(%40adrija.gal)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20borrows%20from%20the%20126%20types%20of%20marble%20that%20went%20into%20its%20making.%20And%20if%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20tick%20the%20box%20for%20sheer%20ingenuity%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335593%2Fpadma-shri-jagdish-and-kamla-mittal-museum-of-indian-art-hyderabad-indian-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehost%20of%20collections%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20the%20museum%20will.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20mansion%20is%20coloured%20and%20traces%20back%20to%20Raja%20Rajendra%20Mullick%2C%20a%20Bengali%20merchant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdopted%20by%20Nilmani%20Mullick%20who%20was%20a%20descendant%20of%20businessman%20Ramakrishna%20Mullick%2C%20Rajendra%20did%20not%20want%20for%20anything.%20In%201878%2C%20Lord%20Lytton%2C%20viceroy%20and%20governor-general%2C%20conferred%20him%20with%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Raja%20Bahadur%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20tender%20age%20of%2016%2C%20Rajendra%20began%20building%20the%20Marble%20Palace%2C%20completing%20it%20by%201840.%20Today%2C%20the%20grand%20avenue%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20love%20for%20cultures%2C%20artistic%20prowess%2C%20and%20penchant%20for%20collectables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrandness%20has%20its%20moments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20are%20fortunate%20to%20be%20privy%20to%20the%20royal%20facades%20and%20interiors%20at%20the%20Marble%20Palace.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20permitted%20a%20private%20guided%20tour%20through%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20possible%20only%20by%20applying%20through%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Tourism%20Information%20Bureau%20%E2%80%94%20prepare%20to%20be%20stunned.%20The%20magic%20lies%20in%20the%20chiselled%20details.%20Privacy%20is%20prized%20at%20this%2019th-century%20home%2C%20which%20explains%20the%20stringent%20rules%20about%20having%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20lucky%20few%20who%20have%20been%20within%20its%20chambers%2C%20speak%20highly%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-goa-maharashtra-sawantwadi-palace-hotel-run-by-royal-family-sawant-bhonsle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epalace%E2%80%99s%20testament%20to%20preserving%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20look%20long%20enough%20at%20the%20block%20of%20white%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20blend%20of%20different%20architectural%20styles%20that%20have%20gone%20into%20its%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neoclassical%20style%20Corinthian%20columns%20blended%20with%20fretwork%20verandahs%20and%20sloping%20roofs%20inspired%20by%20Chinese%20architecture%2C%20give%20way%20to%20Victorian%20furniture%20inside%20the%20home.%20The%20roof%20meanwhile%20is%20topped%20with%20an%20ornately%20carved%20French%20pediment.%20The%20palatial%20quarters%20boast%20five%20halls%3A%20Reception%20Hall%2C%20Painting%20Room%2C%20Sculpture%20Room%2C%20Billiards%20Room%20and%20%3Cem%3EThakur%20Dalan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(place%20of%20worship).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20these%20rooms%20bears%20the%20nostalgia%20of%20the%20art%20that%20Rajendra%20collected%20along%20his%20travels.%20He%20loved%20dabbling%20in%20it%3B%20the%20Bohemian%20goblets%2C%20French%20Ormulo%20clocks%2C%20swords%20from%20Toledo%2C%20and%20Venetian%20mirrors%20are%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F146531%2Fnews-world-ethnic-day-15-must-have-ethnic-souvenirs-from-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esouvenirs%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren%E2%80%99t%20delighting%20your%20senses%2C%20huge%20oil%20paintings%20will.%20These%20include%20Rubens%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98The%20Marriage%20of%20St%20Catherine%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Infant%20Hercules%20Strangling%20the%20Serpent%E2%80%99%20by%20Joshua%20Reynolds%2C%20paintings%20by%20Raja%20Ravi%20Varma%2C%20Jan%20Van%20Goyen%2C%20and%20Giovanni%20Battista%2C%20and%20sculptures%20of%20Venus%2C%20Apollo%2C%20Homer%2C%20and%20other%20mythical%20and%20real%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20the%20palace%20houses%2076%20rare%20artworks%20brought%20from%20Italy%20and%20Belgium%20in%201830%2C%20and%20a%20two-cornered%20biocome%20that%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20worn%20by%20Napoleon%20Bonaparte%20during%20his%20military%20campaigns.%20The%20originality%20is%20still%20debated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20way%20will%20be%20illuminated%20by%20the%20light%20bouncing%20off%20the%2019th-century%20disco%20balls.%20The%20palace%20is%20a%20balance%20between%20grandeur%20and%20a%20warm%20place%20called%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99.%20But%20while%20it%20is%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20touch%20for%20artefacts%20that%20draws%20visitors%20to%20the%20place%2C%20it%20was%20once%20the%20zoo%20that%20made%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Marble%20Palace%20is%20a%20palatial%20nineteenth-century%20mansion%20in%20North%20Kolkata%20at%2046%2C%20Muktaram%20Babu%20Street.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best-preserved%20mansions%20of%20nineteenth-century%20Calcutta.%20The%20mansion%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20marble%20walls%2C%20floors%2C%20and%20sculptures%2C%20from%20which%20it%20derives%20its%20name.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM7cvGln1tn%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FM7cvGln1tn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rupak%20Chattopadhyay%20(%40RupakChatto)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRupakChatto%2Fstatus%2F1712823180560080902%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMagpies%20and%20golden%20pheasants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EHirendra%20Mullick%20%E2%80%94%20resident%20and%20curator%20of%20Marble%20Palace%20%E2%80%94%20credited%20Mullick%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dbotanist%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dbotanist%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIHCAEQIRigATIHCAIQIRigAdIBCDQzNzFqMGo0qAIAsAIA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebackground%2