.%20Keep%20one%20source%20for%20revision%20and%20add%20all%20your%20new%20learnings%20in%20the%20same%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Make%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F225591%2Fupsc-cse-prelims-2020-ias-shashank-topper-notes-general-studies-current-affairs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enotes%20syllabus-wise%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20add%20new%20points%20in%20your%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FRishabh-Bhola-1716536976.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FRishabh-Bhola-1716536976.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FRishabh-Bhola-1716536976-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FRishabh-Bhola-1716536976-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FRishabh-Bhola-1716536976-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FRishabh-Bhola-1716536976-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351071%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20length%20of%20the%20notes%20per%20subject%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20subjective.%20However%2C%20for%20bigger%20subjects%2C%20my%20notes%20were%20around%2035%20pages%2C%20and%20for%20smaller%20subjects%20around%2010%20to%2012%20pages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Collect%20words%20that%20can%20be%20fitted%20in%20most%20of%20the%20questions.%20For%20instance%2C%20decentralisation%2C%20politicisation%2C%20and%20representation%20merged%20with%20words%20of%20the%20syllabus%2C%20like%20h